<div id="p148" class="blockpost roweven">
	<h2><span><span class="conr">#2&nbsp;</span><a href="viewtopic.php?pid=148#p148">28-Aug-2009,Fri 11:58:10</a></span></h2>
	<div class="box">
		<div class="inbox">
			<div class="postleft">
				<dl>
					<dt><strong><a href="profile.php?id=3">higopi</a></strong></dt>
					<dd class="usertitle"><strong>Expert Member</strong></dd>
					<dd class="postavatar"><img src="img/avatars/3.jpg" width="60" height="60" alt="" /></dd>
				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3> Re: Need help in Transliteration</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>Hi Karthizen,<br /><br />Its pretty simple to transliterate Hindi to English. For each combination of Hindi letter, you need to create a Hashmap with respective combination of English letters. And then you need to create a function which will read the complete Hindi text and refer to the hashmap and then transliterate one letter at a time.<br /><br />Can you please elaborate which encoding you are using for the Hindi text?</p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Thanks,<br /><br />Gopi<br />Pick any two of &quot;Quality, Quick, Cheap&quot; service from me.</div>
			</div>
